title: Roland JV-1010 Module w/ Expansion
description:
Compact sound module with 64-voice polyphony
1,023 patches from the JV-2080 sound module and the “Session” expansion board
1 expansion slot for additional SR-JV80-Series wave expansion board
Reverb, chorus, plus 40 multi-EFX
Intuitive user interface with knob-based control
1/2 rack design
Phrase Preview for hearing a selected sound in a musical phrase
SoundFinder Categories
GM compatible

Includes Keyboards of the 60’s & 70’s expansion (SR-JV80-08)
